metadata.name: Supergiants #2
metadata.description: Supergiants is a collection of 5555 NFTs of the most important and influential CEOs in the world that, thanks to their long term vision and entrepreneurial skills, managed to revolutionize our lives. It consists of 18 unique CEOs and 12 easter eggs, with more than 200 attributes.

attributes.trait_type: How awesome am I, from 1 to 10?
